column2: "I'm only slightly injured. Please pay me no mind. Please, don't be kind to me."
"I am not worthy of such treatment. Ten years ago, I lost all rights to it."
"No, until he can trust another person again... I..."
"Sina, what in the world are you rambling on about?"
"If you can run your mouth that much, then get back to work!"
"And you! Don't go poking your nose where it doesn't belong. I don't want to have kill you before you're ready."
